headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Nasdaq’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Nasdaq’s fourth quarter exceeded Wall Street’s expectations, with management attributing the strong performance to robust growth in its solutions businesses and record activity across its U.S. and European exchanges.
